            <title>[SOLR-16457] solr.data.home should not be set to empty string in bin/solr</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16457</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;solr.data.home should not be set to empty string in bin/solr since that causes the security.policy to be more wide open than it should. &lt;/p&gt;

