                            <comment id="17630100" author="risdenk" created="Tue, 8 Nov 2022 00:28:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is causing issues that &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=elyograg&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;elyograg&quot;&gt;elyograg&lt;/a&gt; found where installer doesn&apos;t work with symlink installed. See details here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://the-asf.slack.com/archives/CEKUCUNE9/p1667834706364199&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://the-asf.slack.com/archives/CEKUCUNE9/p1667834706364199&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
